      "text": [
        "2169 - وَ رُوِيَ : «أَنَّ مَنْ أَرَادَ أَنْ يَكْثُرَ مَالُهُ فَلْيُطِلِ اَلْوُقُوفَ عَلَى اَلصَّفَا وَ اَلْمَرْوَةِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2169 - It has been narrated: \"Whoever wishes to increase their wealth should prolong their standing on Safa and Marwah.\""
        ]
      }
    }
